# Local secrets for `wrangler pages dev` (the Cloudflare function runtime).
# Copy this file to  .dev.vars  and paste your real Planning Center
# Personal Access Token values. .dev.vars is gitignored — it never gets committed.
#
# Get these at: https://api.planningcenteronline.com/oauth/applications
#   → Personal Access Tokens → New Personal Access Token
PCO_APP_ID=PCO_APP_ID
PCO_SECRET=PCO_SECRET